" .. "BAT %4.0f
" .. "RPM %4.0f
" .. "TEMP %4.0f

screen.drawText(0,0,str)
end

object.script:
function gn(n) return input.getNumber(n) end
function sb(n,v) output.setBool(n,v) end
function gb(n) return input.getBool(n) end
function sn(n,v) output.setNumber(n,v) end
function clamp(n, low, high) return math.min(math.max(n, low), high) end
zoomq=5
function onTick()
sb(32,gb(32))
enabled=gb(3) -- if not enabled then return end gpsx=gn(1) gpsy=gn(2) compass=gn(3) hdg=(compass*-360)%360 waypointx=gn(4) waypointy=gn(5)
dx=waypointx-gpsx dy=waypointy-gpsy local b=(math.pi/2) - math.atan(dy,dx) b=(b+(math.pi*2)) % (math.pi*2) bearing=b*180/math.pi sn(4,bearing)
sn(3,compass) zoomm=gn(32) sn(32,zoomm) zoom=zoomm/1000 halfkm=zoomm/2 end
zoom=1
function onDraw()
-- debug -- screen.setColor(255,255,255) -- screen.drawText(0,0,string.format("%.0f",scr))
if not enabled then return end w=screen.getWidth() h=screen.getHeight() cx=w/2 cy=h/2
screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawClear()
screen.drawMap(gpsx,gpsy,zoom)
-- Draw self blip in center of map screen.setColor(0,255,0) local t=-compass*math.pi*2 screen.drawLine(cx,cy,cx+math.sin(t)*5, cy-math.cos(t)*5)
screen.setColor(255,0,0) screen.drawCircleF(cx,cy,1)
-- Draw waypoint blip screen.setColor(0,0,255)
-- screen.drawCircleF(cx + dx * w / zoomm, cy + dy * h/zoomm, 2) wx,wy=map.mapToScreen(gpsx,gpsy,zoom,w,h,waypointx,waypointy) screen.drawCircleF(wx, wy, 2)
dist=math.sqrt(dx*dx+dy*dy)
if dist<1000 then distfmt="%3.0fM" else distfmt="%3.0fKM" dist=dist/1000 end
screen.setColor(0,0,255) local txt = string.format("BRNG: %3.0f\nDIST: " .. distfmt .. "\n%.0f, %.0f\n%.0fkm",bearing,dist,gpsx,gpsy,zoom) screen.drawText(0,0,txt) end

object.script:
function gn(n) return input.getNumber(n) end
function dl(ax,ay,bx,by) screen.drawLine(ax,ay,bx,by) end
hfov=property.getNumber("hud h fov") hfovrad=hfov/180*math.pi hhfovrad=hfovrad/2 hradscale=math.sin(hfovrad)
crossy=property.getNumber("crosshair y") crossleg=2 crossgap=3 hcrossgap=crossgap/2
function crosshair(x,y) screen.drawLine(x,y-hcrossgap,x,y-hcrossgap-crossleg) screen.drawLine(x,y+hcrossgap,x,y+hcrossgap+crossleg) screen.drawLine(x-hcrossgap,y,x-hcrossgap-crossleg,y) screen.drawLine(x+hcrossgap,y,x+hcrossgap+crossleg,y) end
function onTick() compass=gn(1) bearing=gn(2) ammo=gn(3) end
rowh=6 function onDraw()
local h,b,t,x local w=screen.getWidth() local height=screen.getHeight() local hw=w/2 local hh=height/2
crosshair(hw,hh+crossy)
h=compass*math.pi*2 b=bearing*math.pi/180 t=(h+b)%(math.pi*2)
dx=math.sin(t)/hradscale*w x=hw+dx
screen.setColor(0,64,0) -- screen.drawText(0,0,string.format("%0.1f",hfov))
if math.abs(dx)>hw then if x>=w then dl(w-1,2,w-3,0) dl(w-1,2,w-3,4) else dl(0,2,2,0) dl(0,2,2,4) end else dl(x,0,x,2) end
-- center mark dl(hw,3,hw,4)
-- Ammo counter screen.drawText(0,height-rowh,string.format("%4.0f",ammo)) end
